| Significantly positive | 0.4233 | 0.0000 | 0.0000 |
| Not sure | 0.0042 | 0.0367 | 0.0000 |
| **Expected Impact (QEB_2)** | | | |
| Significantly negative | 0.0000 | 0.0000 | 0.2960 |
